{"tid":2024009,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東京增5宗確診 政府稱需全面研究是否撤銷緊急事態","createTime":"2020-05-19T11:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T11:09:01.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb2cbd1080e102cde71fb797c1ad76deae5cc4d","tid":2024009,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"東京增5宗確診 政府稱需全面研究是否撤銷緊急事態<br />\n2020-05-19 HKT 16:20<br />\n<br />\n日本單日新增31宗新型肺炎確診個案，當中東京佔5宗，是自政府頒布緊急事態令以來的新低。外界關注日本政府在後日重新審視解除東京、大阪、京都等8個都道府縣緊急事態令的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n經濟再生大臣西村康稔在參議院內閣委員會表示，8個地區的感染人數增幅放緩，符合撤銷緊急事態的標準之一，但仍然需要研究包括醫療系統等配套，以全面決定是否撤銷緊急事態，強調當未來的感染人數再次增加時，政府必須以更嚴格的措施去看待疫情。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日本政府通過向受疫情影響而財政困難的約43萬大學生與其他學生，每人派發20萬日圓的現金援助，以支援他們交付學費。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527045-20200519.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527045-20200519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7nPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=d429bf40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527045-20200519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=16ab6d32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527045-20200519.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人最關心的應該係幾時可去日本旅行</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88521d44c8acb4f476e37c4722e17684b47693e6","tid":2024009,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"香港仲限聚緊，人地唔封你再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}